    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but I need to be more specific for my assignment. If you had to recommend actual sentencing directions—like probation vs. incarceration—which way would you lean for each? \n\nSpecifically, for Defendant B, does the \"sporadic employment\" and \"unstable housing\" make them a higher risk for reoffending compared to Defendant A? I'm trying to see if those factors should shift the focus toward more punitive measures to ensure public safety.",
